.Sh PERFORMANCE TUNING GUIDE
.Ss Runtime tunables (CLI/config)
.Bl -bullet -compact
.It
.Cm threads
: worker threads that execute handlers.
Increase gradually; too high can increase lock contention.
.It
.Cm max_conns
: connection budget.
Must stay below kernel/file-descriptor limits.
.It
.Cm conn_timeout
: idle keep-alive timeout; lower values reclaim sockets faster.
.It
.Cm max_req_size
: hard cap for request header buffering.
.It
.Cm mandoc_timeout
: upper bound for man rendering subprocesses.
.It
.Cm verbose
: keep disabled during benchmarks.
.El
.Ss Compile-time tunables (code constants)
.Bl -bullet -compact
.It
Dispatcher/queue sizing:
.Dv MAX_EVENTS , LISTEN_BACKLOG , QUEUE_CAPACITY , MAX_KEEPALIVE_REQUESTS .
.It
HTTP write path:
.Dv WRITE_RETRY_LIMIT , WRITE_WAIT_MS .
.It
Static asset cache:
.Dv FILE_CACHE_SHARDS , FILE_CACHE_SLOTS , FILE_CACHE_MAX_BYTES ,
.Dv FILE_CACHE_INSERTS_PER_SEC , FILE_CACHE_MAX_AGE_SEC .
.It
Module ring buffers:
.Dv METRICS_RING_BYTES , NETWORK_RING_BYTES , PKG_RING_BYTES .
.El
.Ss Caching strategy summary
.Bl -bullet -compact
.It
Template cache: preloaded at startup, refreshed every 60s.
.It
Hot view cache: 5 slots, 10s TTL.
.It
Static file cache: 16 shards × 32 slots, 256 KiB max, 120s TTL.
.It
Metrics ring: 1MB, 1s samples, 120-sample history.
.It
Networking ring: 1MB, 1s samples, pre-built JSON snapshot.
.It
Man page cache: 16×128 slots, 600s TTL, filesystem fallback.
.It
Package ring: 2MB, 30s TTL, on-demand population.
.El
